messages.message:
Hi all! We managed to fix the ECR issue (ty @Abhinav ++ and @astpierre ++)

Immediate fix is to modify  `~/.docker/config.json` in your sandbox to add:

```{
	"credHelpers": {
		"gcr.io": "gcloud",
        "549230430157.dkr.ecr.us-east-2.amazonaws.com": "ecr-login"
	}
}```
I will work on updating the base image as well.

Update: With this change, you do not need the ecr-login script anymore
